  "recaps": {
    "1": "The Night Court works to rebuild and heal in the months following their victory over Hybern, with everyone struggling to adjust to peace.",
    "2": "Feyre and Rhysand balance their duties as rulers with their own trauma recovery, while Nesta isolates herself and drinks heavily.",
    "3": "Cassian works with Illyrian war veterans while trying to reach out to Nesta, who continues to push everyone away.",
    "4": "Azriel struggles with his feelings for Elain while maintaining his spymaster duties in the more peaceful but still complex political landscape.",
    "5": "Morrigan focuses on building new diplomatic and trade relationships while organizing celebrations to help everyone heal.",
    "6": "Lucien splits his time between courts, learning about his Day Court heritage while respecting Elain's continued rejection.",
    "7": "Varian visits from the Summer Court to court Amren, helping build stronger relationships between the courts.",
    "8": "The Inner Circle works together to help war refugees and survivors, showing how their family bond helps them serve others.",
    "9": "Elain finds solace in domestic activities like gardening and cooking, slowly rebuilding her sense of purpose and identity.",
    "10": "Preparations begin for Winter Solstice celebrations, with everyone hoping the festivities will bring healing and joy.",
    "11": "Family dynamics become clearer as everyone works through their trauma in different ways, some healthier than others.",
    "12": "Relationships develop and change as people learn to live in peace rather than constant preparation for war.",
    "13": "Winter Solstice celebrations begin, bringing together friends, family, and allies to share in joy and gratitude.",
    "14": "Gift-giving and celebrations reveal the depth of love and care within the chosen family of the Inner Circle.",
    "15": "The joy and warmth of the celebrations help everyone remember what they fought for and what peace can offer.",
    "16": "Personal conversations during the celebrations reveal ongoing struggles and growth among all the family members.",
    "17": "Moments of genuine happiness and laughter show that healing is possible even after the darkest experiences.",
    "18": "The success of the celebrations demonstrates how community and love can overcome trauma and build hope.",
    "19": "Relationships deepen as people allow themselves to be vulnerable and open in the safety of peace and family.",
    "20": "Plans for the future begin to take shape as everyone starts to believe that lasting peace might actually be possible.",
    "21": "The Winter Solstice ends with hope and determination to build a better world, setting the stage for future growth and challenges."
